  "slug": "cheddar-rosemary-spiralized-potato-pancakes",
  "title": "Cheddar-Rosemary Spiralized Potato Pancakes",
  "subtitle": "A cake worth the weighing.",
  "excerpt": "Cheddar-Rosemary Spiralized Potato Pancakes. A baking recipe from Rebecca's collection, straightforward, reliable, worth weighing rather than scooping.",
  "type": "RECIPE",
  "sourceNotes": "From Rebecca's personal cookbook, a recipe she's made many times in her own kitchen.",
  "body": {
    "type": "doc",
    "content": [
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "An American family-table recipe. Generous and warming, built for a crowd. The amounts adjust to suit what you need.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Cake batters reward weighing over scooping. Room-temperature butter and eggs, raised properly, tested with a skewer.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 2
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "What you need",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
